<br>
The spoiler at - <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.eqdruids.com/pop/hall_of_honor.htm">www.eqdruids.com/pop/hall_of_honor.htm</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> is correct from the point they pick up the quest. However, they have the start wrong and if you don't follow the quest exactly as it is supposed to go, you will lose your hearts/shards and the quest mobs won't respond to you properly. You absolutely have to do every step or you lose you items.<br>
<br>
Here is the difference:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Find Johon Popoah and hail him twice.</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
The guys name is actually Sergeant Johnson Popoah. Hail him once then say &quot;what compound&quot; then hail him again.<br>
<br>
If you don't do this part in that order, Paralin Notion will not answer your hail (he will give the quest text if prompted but you won't be able to advance if he doesn't ask you if you are brave or stupid) and Master Sergeant Aaramis Daryln won't talk to you at all.<br>
<br>
